summary: Teleports the Player. Great mod when playing the game while fast travel is disabled.
descriptionHtml:
Great Mod if you are planning to play the Game while fast travel is disabled.
Added 10 Teleport Stones. You can start using the Teleport Stones after joining the mages guild.
However, you need to discover your destination Stone in order to Teleport to it.
Cities: Dawnstar, Falkreath, Morthal and Winterhold.
Towns: Dragon Bridge, Ivarstead, Riverwood and Rorikstead.
Settlements: High Hrothgar and Fort Dawnguard.
author: Gus
